parent1.code: a photo of a black panther prowling in the style of film noir. It slinks through shadows on the city rooftops in the urban jungle on a moonlit night, eyes gleaming, with streetlamps casting long shadows and fog rolling in.

offspring.code: A photograph of a black panther prowling menacingly in the style of classic film noir. It slinks stealthily on the gritty, decaying rooftops in the sprawling urban jungle on a chilly night, its piercing emerald eyes gleaming with predatory intent, with flickering streetlamps casting long shadows and thick fog rolling ominously in.
